alerts.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued December 15 at 12:06AM PST until December 15 at 10:00AM PST by NWS Los Angeles/Oxnard CA
alerts.description:
* WHAT...Visibility one quarter mile or less in dense fog.

* WHERE...Santa Ynez Valley and Southern Salinas Valley.

* WHEN...Until 10 AM PST this morning.

* IMPACTS...Low visibility could make driving conditions hazardous.
